    "more": "Each node represents an <a href='https://ideas.repec.org/i/etwitter.html'>economist registered on RePEc and on Twitter</a>. Edges (links) show whether a user follows or is followed by another user. Colors represent the user's main research area, based on an aggregation of their main <a href='https://ideas.repec.org/n/'>NEP field</a>. In order to keep things manageable, the 95 NEP fields were aggregated into 15 fields. The match between NEP fields and groups is defined in <a href='https://github.com/chrMongeau/repec-twitter/blob/master/NEP.csv'>https://github.com/chrMongeau/repec-twitter/blob/master/NEP.csv</a>. The size of nodes reflects user's centrality (PageRank) in the network.<p>More info here: <a href='https://github.com/chrMongeau/repec-twitter'>https://github.com/chrMongeau/repec-twitter</a>.",
